	<a href="http://www.rae.org/AI.html">Artificial Intelligence and the Creator</a>.&nbsp; An odd article, in both location (a site designed for the refutation of evolution) and its interesting challenge concerning Christian theology and the prospect of an intelligent machine.  Some interesting items to think about on the AI question.<br>
