	<a name="89286281">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www-formal.stanford.edu/jmc/reviews/weizenbaum/node7.html">What Worries about Computers are Warranted?</a>.&nbsp; This is part of a review of Weizenbaum that touches on the worries that need to be considered.  The review is by John McCarthy, and he asserts that all of these concerns can be assuaged.  Pointed out by classmate Thomas Eichberger.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#89286281">Monday, February 17, 2003</a></span></div>
